== About me 
Before coming to Fudan, I completed my Ph.D. in School of Physics at [http://www.bit.edu.cn/ Beijing Institute of Technology], 
where I worked with [http://physics.bit.edu.cn/szdw/zzjzg/fg/lyl/index.htm Prof. Yulong Liu]. Before that, I received B.E. in School of Information and Communication Engineering from [http://www.njit.edu.cn/ Nanjing Institute of Technology].

